{"id":1219,"date":"2025-04-11T01:00:37","date_gmt":"2025-04-10T18:00:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1219"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:39:13","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:39:13","slug":"mesotherapy-mun","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/mesotherapy-mun\/","title":{"rendered":"Mesotherapy m\u1ee5n s\u1ea7n, m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p cho m\u1ee5n s\u1ea9n m\u1ee7 nh\u1eb9, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng, m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to, s\u1eb9o r\u1ed7 sau tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>X\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ee5n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111a ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u01b0u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng.<\/li>\n<li>T\u00e1i t\u1ea1o, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m sau m\u1ee5n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Mesotherapy m\u1ee5n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt ti\u00eam vi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n (nh\u01b0 kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n, vitamin, kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t) v\u00e0o t\u1ea7ng trung b\u00ec c\u1ee7a da &#8211; n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u, ti\u00eau vi\u00eam, gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi b\u00f4i ngo\u00e0i da.<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee5n to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea3 4 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n v\u1edbi t\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u1ed1c Sulfur 2.28%, Retinol 0.05%, Bakuchiol 2%.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng b\u1ed9 &#8220;ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n&#8221; t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n, kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n m\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 45 ph\u00fat<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng 05 bu\u1ed5i, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb 21 &#8211; 28 ng\u00e0y, trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1ch nhau 14 ng\u00e0y<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -5px; top: 93.3153px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p cho m\u1ee5n s\u1ea9n m\u1ee7 nh\u1eb9, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng, m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to, s\u1eb9o r\u1ed7 sau tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3581,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[57],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1219","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-meso-therapy","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1219","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1219"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3581"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1219"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/g